dp:SF_Metadata_Contract a owl:NamedIndividual ;
    rdfs:label "SF Metadata Contract"@en ;
    dctm:description "Defines the semantics, ownership, and expected quality for video metadata. Intended users: ingestion pipeline, discovery services, analytics consumers."@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Key entities: Video, Channel, Creator, Tag, Category. Required fields: video_id, creator_id, upload_timestamp, duration_seconds. Recommended: language, topic_tags. Change policy: breaking changes only on major version increments."@en,
        "Story: As a discovery engineer, I need consistent video_id, creator_id, upload time, and duration so search and ranking can join metadata reliably without brittle ad-hoc mappings."@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """SF Metadata Contract has description Defines the semantics, ownership, and expected quality for video metadata. Intended users: ingestion pipeline, discovery services, analytics consumers.
SF Metadata Contract rdfs:comment Key entities: Video, Channel, Creator, Tag, Category. Required fields: video_id, creator_id, upload_timestamp, duration_seconds. Recommended: language, topic_tags. Change policy: breaking changes only on major version increments.
SF Metadata Contract rdfs:comment Story: As a discovery engineer, I need consistent video_id, creator_id, upload time, and duration so search and ranking can join metadata reliably without brittle ad-hoc mappings.
SF Metadata Contract has label SF Metadata Contract."""@en .

dp:SF_Metadata_Quality a owl:NamedIndividual ;
    rdfs:label "SF Metadata Quality"@en ;
    dctm:description "Completeness, consistency, and timeliness metrics for core video metadata fields."@en ;
    rdfs:comment "Completeness: required fields present for >= 99.5% of records daily. Consistency: video_id↔creator_id alignment >= 99.9%. Timeliness: ingest-to-availability median < 5 min, P95 < 15 min."@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """SF Metadata Quality has description Completeness, consistency, and timeliness metrics for core video metadata fields.
SF Metadata Quality rdfs:comment Completeness: required fields present for >= 99.5% of records daily. Consistency: video_id↔creator_id alignment >= 99.9%. Timeliness: ingest-to-availability median < 5 min, P95 < 15 min.
SF Metadata Quality has label SF Metadata Quality."""@en .

