docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_01 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 01"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 1 ;
    docs:chunk_text "StreamForge creator engagement improved in Q3 2025, but gains were uneven across creator cohorts and upload frequencies. This report summarizes creator-side engagement metrics, highlights drivers of change, and proposes data product improvements for Q4."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Summary"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 01 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 01 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 01."""@en .

docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_02 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 02"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 2 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Reporting period: Q3 2025 (2025-07-01 to 2025-09-30). Population: active creators with at least one upload in the last 90 days. Exclusions: policy-removed channels and test accounts."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Scope and time window"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 02 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 02 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 02."""@en .

docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_03 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 03"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 3 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Monthly active creators (MAC): +6.2%. Uploads per active creator: +3.1%. Creator retention (90-day): +1.4 pp. Creator time-to-first-view median improved from 46 minutes to 39 minutes. Creator monetization enrollment: flat (+0.2%)."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Key metrics (Q3 vs Q2)"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 03 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 03 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 03."""@en .

docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_04 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 04"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 4 ;
    docs:chunk_text "1) Faster time-to-first-view correlated strongly with higher creator retention, especially for small channels (<10k subscribers). 2) Improvements concentrated in long-form video; short-form creators did not see comparable lift."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Drivers and observations (1–2)"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 04 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 04 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 04."""@en .

docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_05 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 05"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 5 ;
    docs:chunk_text "3) Metadata completeness (title, tags, category) was the strongest predictor of search impressions for new uploads. 4) The creator onboarding funnel had a measurable drop at connect payout account, but this is outside the primary scope of this report."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Drivers and observations (3–4)"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 05 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 05 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 05."""@en .

docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_06 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 06"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 6 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Intermittent missing tag fields in the video metadata feed during August. A small fraction of creator profiles contained stale country codes after an upstream identity change. Issues did not materially change Q3 directional results, but reduce confidence in cohort segmentation."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Data quality notes"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 06 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 06 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 06."""@en .

docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_07 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 07"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 7 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Prioritize the Video Metadata data product to improve completeness and freshness of tags and categories. Add a creator-facing metadata quality indicator. Publish a weekly Creator Engagement Snapshot. Add SLAs for metadata freshness and completeness aligned with creator experience metrics (time-to-first-view and impressions)."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Recommendations for Q4"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 07 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 07 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 07."""@en .

docs:Creator_Engagement_Report_Q3_2025_Chunk_08 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 08"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 8 ;
    docs:chunk_text "How much of time-to-first-view improvement came from ranking changes vs metadata improvements? Can we isolate the short-form creator cohort and design targeted metadata guidance?"@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Open questions"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 08 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 08 has label Creator Engagement Report Q3 2025 Chunk 08."""@en .

docs:Creator_Growth_Metric_Definition_Memo_2026_Chunk_01 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 01"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 1 ;
    docs:chunk_text """The Creator Growth metric is an executive KPI intended to summarize whether the StreamForge creator ecosystem is expanding in a sustainable way. It is designed for high-level dashboards and strategic reporting, not for diagnosing individual creator performance.

The metric is sensitive to both creator supply (how many creators are producing content and reaching engagement thresholds) and audience demand (whether viewers are engaging with creator content). It should be interpreted alongside supporting KPIs such as retention, new creator onboarding, and content category mix."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "What the metric is for"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 01 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 01 has label Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 01."""@en .

docs:Creator_Growth_Metric_Definition_Memo_2026_Chunk_02 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 02"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 2 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Conceptually, Creator Growth increases when:
- more creators cross the 'active creator' threshold,
- existing creators increase their sustained engagement,
- and the distribution of engagement is not dominated by a tiny number of outliers.

A simple (illustrative) construction combines:
- count of active creators,
- median engagement per creator,
- and growth rate of creator cohorts over a reporting window.

Exact parameter values and thresholds are maintained as part of the metric specification and may evolve with governance review."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Definition (conceptual)"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 02 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 02 has label Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 02."""@en .

docs:Creator_Growth_Metric_Definition_Memo_2026_Chunk_03 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 03"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 3 ;
    docs:chunk_text """The computation is derived from the SF Creator Insights Dataset. Required inputs include creator-level KPIs such as:
- play counts
- unique viewers
- engagement rate
- retention proxies

Because the metric is computed from aggregated creator KPIs, upstream data quality issues (missing events, broken joins) typically manifest as sudden metric discontinuities. The computation run should therefore enforce strict validation on input freshness and completeness."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Computation inputs"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 03 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 03 has label Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 03."""@en .

docs:Creator_Growth_Metric_Definition_Memo_2026_Chunk_04 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 04"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 4 ;
    docs:chunk_text """The executive dashboard uses a reporting window aligned to business cadence (e.g., trailing 28 days). The computation run applies this window to creator KPIs, aggregates to the metric level, and publishes a snapshot.

Snapshots are versioned by date and should be treated as immutable. If a recomputation is required (e.g., backfill corrections), publish a new snapshot with a new version identifier rather than overwriting historical values."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Windowing and snapshot logic"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 04 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 04 has label Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 04."""@en .

docs:Creator_Growth_Metric_Definition_Memo_2026_Chunk_05 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 05"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 5 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Interpretation guidelines:
- Short-term volatility may occur due to product experiments, seasonal effects, or data pipeline incidents.
- A sustained increase over multiple windows is stronger evidence of ecosystem growth.
- Compare the metric against segment-level analyses (e.g., demographics and region) to understand *where* growth is happening.

Governance note: if metric definitions change, the change must be communicated to consumers and recorded in a data contract so that historical comparisons remain meaningful."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Interpretation guidance"@en ;
    docs:has_topic dp:Contract ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 05 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 05 has label Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 05."""@en .

docs:Creator_Growth_Metric_Definition_Memo_2026_Chunk_06 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 06"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 6 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Related analyses include:
- Play video demographics summary (Q1–Q4 2025)
- Creator Insights aggregation runbook
- Regional acquisition and retention decomposition

These documents together support RAG-style question answering such as: 'How is Creator Growth computed?', 'What data feeds the metric?', and 'What demographic shifts occurred in 2025 that may affect creator growth?'"""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Link to related analyses"@en ;
    docs:has_topic docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026,
        docs:Play_Video_Demographics_Quarterly_Report_2025 ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 06 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 06 has label Creator Growth Metric Definition Memo 2026 Chunk 06."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_01 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 01"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 1 ;
    docs:chunk_text """The Creator Insights Aggregation produces the SF Creator Insights Dataset, a curated table of creator KPIs used by dashboards, reporting, and downstream metric computations. It consolidates engagement events into creator-level aggregates and applies standard filters, normalization, and windowing.

Primary output: SF Creator Insights Dataset.
Secondary outputs: run metadata, validation summaries, and intermediate aggregates used for debugging."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Purpose and outputs"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 01 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 01 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 01."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_02 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 02"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 2 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Inputs:
- Engagement Events Dataset (event stream, normalized)
- Video Metadata Dataset (video → creator mapping and content attributes)
- Creator Profile Dataset (creator reference data and eligibility flags)

All three inputs are required. If any input fails freshness thresholds, the run is considered degraded and must not publish outputs to production dashboards."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Inputs"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 02 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 02 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 02."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_03 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 03"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 3 ;
    docs:chunk_text """High-level transformation steps:
1) Filter engagement events to eligible events and valid account/video ids.
2) Join events to video metadata to map events to creators.
3) Join to creator profile reference data (tier, region, account status).
4) Aggregate by creator and reporting window to compute KPIs (plays, unique viewers, engagement rate, etc.).
5) Normalize and apply standard definitions (e.g., deduping retry bursts).
6) Publish curated results to SF Creator Insights Dataset."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Transformations (high-level)"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 03 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 03 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 03."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_04 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 04"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 4 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Quality checks include:
- Completeness of joins (event→video, video→creator)
- Distribution checks on key metrics (outliers, zeros, negative values)
- Volume regression checks (unexpected drops/spikes by region)
- Schema conformance validation

Failure handling:
- Hard failures stop the run.
- Soft failures publish output to a quarantine location and alert the Analytics Engineering Team."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Quality checks"@en ;
    docs:has_topic skos:ConceptScheme ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 04 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 04 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 04."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_05 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 05"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 5 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Provenance is recorded using PROV-O:
- The aggregation run is a prov:Activity (dp:Data_Analysis_Activity).
- Input datasets are prov:Entity assets.
- Output dataset is generated by the activity.
- The Analytics Engineering Team is associated with the activity.

This structure enables automated embedding-note generation and supports question answering such as: 'What datasets were used to produce SF Creator Insights?' and 'Which team ran the aggregation?'"""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Provenance and traceability"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 05 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 05 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 05."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_06 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 06"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 6 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Schedule: the aggregation is typically run daily, with additional ad-hoc runs during major product launches.

Operational constraints:
- Completion time target: under 30 minutes.
- Freshness requirements: engagement events must be available within a defined latency window.
- Publishing rules: do not overwrite prior snapshots without a version identifier.

If SLAs are missed, downstream metrics (e.g., Creator Growth) may be stale for dashboards."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Operational schedule and SLAs"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 06 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 06 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 06."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_07 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 07"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 7 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Common failure modes:
- Partial ingestion of engagement events causing artificial volume drops
- Missing video metadata due to upstream schema change
- Creator reference data drift (stale account status)
- Unexpected spikes from client retry storms

Mitigation:
- Validate input dataset freshness and schema before running aggregation.
- Use regression checks on event volumes and join completeness.
- Maintain a rollback plan for publishing outputs."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Common failure modes"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 07 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 07 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 07."""@en .

docs:Creator_Insights_Aggregation_Runbook_2026_Chunk_08 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 08"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 8 ;
    docs:chunk_text """Downstream consumers include:
- Executive dashboards that display creator KPIs
- Metric computations such as Creator Growth
- Ad-hoc analyses (demographics, regional trends)

Because downstream systems assume stable KPI definitions, changes to the aggregation logic must be coordinated via a data contract and communicated to consumers before deployment."""@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Downstream dependencies"@en ;
    docs:has_topic dp:Contract ;
    dp:embedding_note """Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 08 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 08 has label Creator Insights Aggregation Runbook 2026 Chunk 08."""@en .

