sf:Ads_Revenue_Reconciliation_Notes_Nov_2025_Chunk_01 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 01"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 1 ;
    docs:chunk_text "This note documents how daily ad revenue is reconciled between delivery logs and finance reporting. The goal is consistent numbers across dashboards and the general ledger."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Context"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 01 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 01 has label Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 01."""@en .

sf:Ads_Revenue_Reconciliation_Notes_Nov_2025_Chunk_02 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 02"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 2 ;
    docs:chunk_text "We used the StreamForge Ads Performance data product. It provides daily aggregates by video and channel, sourced from ad server logs and summarized into BigQuery tables."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Data sources"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 02 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 02 has label Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 02."""@en .

sf:Ads_Revenue_Reconciliation_Notes_Nov_2025_Chunk_03 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 03"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 3 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Late-arriving events and currency conversion updates can shift revenue totals. A 'finalized_date' convention is recommended so stakeholders know when a day’s revenue is stable."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Known pitfalls"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 03 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 03 has label Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 03."""@en .

sf:Ads_Revenue_Reconciliation_Notes_Nov_2025_Chunk_04 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 04"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 4 ;
    docs:chunk_text "The dataset is at daily grain. Video_id and channel_id are stable join keys. Avoid joining to event-level engagement without first aggregating engagement to daily grain."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Join keys and grain"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 04 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 04 has label Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 04."""@en .

sf:Ads_Revenue_Reconciliation_Notes_Nov_2025_Chunk_05 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 05"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 5 ;
    docs:chunk_text "We validate that delivered impressions reconcile to billed impressions within 0.5%. Outliers are investigated by country, device, and ad format."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Validation checks"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 05 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 05 has label Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 05."""@en .

sf:Ads_Revenue_Reconciliation_Notes_Nov_2025_Chunk_06 a owl:NamedIndividual,
        docs:Document_Chunk ;
    rdfs:label "Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 06"@en ;
    docs:chunk_index 6 ;
    docs:chunk_text "Publish a documented 'ads_revenue_daily' view as the canonical table for reporting. Deprecate ad-hoc spreadsheets and require dashboard owners to reference the canonical view."@en ;
    docs:chunk_title "Governance recommendation"@en ;
    dp:embedding_note """Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 06 is an instance of Document Chunk.
Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 06 has label Ads Revenue Reconciliation Notes Nov 2025 Chunk 06."""@en .

